{"hadithnumber": "1251", "arabic": "حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا غُنْدَرٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ شُعْبَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏ع", "grades": "{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Munkar'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Munkar'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}", "reference": "Book 5, Hadith 449", "international_number": "1251", "narrator_chain": ""}
