{"hadithnumber": "1374", "arabic": "حَدَّثَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏ وَأَبُو عُمَرَ حَفْصُ بْنُ عُمَرَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَا:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّ", "grades": "{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Very Daif'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Very Daif'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Very Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}", "reference": "Book 5, Hadith 572", "international_number": "1374", "narrator_chain": ""}
